    <briefdescription>
<para>A command that encapsulates a UI action request. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>UiActionCommands are submitted when UI elements are activated (e.g., button pressed, menu item selected). They carry the source entity and the action identifier to execute.</para>
